    "en": {
      "title": "Peradeniya University Counselor died after falling from Saradial rock",
      "author": "unknown",
      "body_lines": [
        "According to the police, a support instructor of the Faculty of Agriculture of the University of Peradeniya, who climbed the Mawanella Uthum Kanda Surasaradiyal rock with a group of students from the University of Peradeniya, slipped from the rock and fell down a 300-foot cliff and died.",
        "A 27-year-old girl named Virasmi Kodituvakku, a resident of Elpitiya, has died.",
        "The police say that while a group of students from the Faculty of Agriculture of the University of Peradeniya were climbing Uthumkanda Surasaradian Rock this morning, she slipped and fell down like this."
      ],
